{"tid":1747382,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"我地好似有樣嘢無做？？","createTime":"2019-11-23T07:47:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T18:53:29.000Z","uid":320074,"like":82,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"30fc93de171543c7462b32c56d61acf3adb743aa","tid":1747382,"uid":320074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:47:02.000Z","msg":"唔知大家有無發現。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地好似忽略咗班少數族裔選民？</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">先唔講選舉有無用</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但作為社會一分子，我地唔係應該俾足夠既選舉資訊啲少數族裔，去選自己心儀既候選人？</span></span><br />\n雖然我講呢句可能有啲遲，但希望大家<br />\n喺<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">僅於既時間，製作翻啲英文文宣俾佢地</span></span><br />\n記住，光復香港<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">並非只係屬於我地香港人</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">更加係讓唔同族裔既人感受到歸屬感，一同捍衛我城</span><br />\n<br />\n都係果句，我理得你覺得選舉有無用<br />\n但請記得，大家要記得翻我地既同行者<br />\n包括 歪果仁、新移民同埋少數族裔<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">同行者，均為香港人。</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">呢場革命，一個都不能少。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n最後一句，保皇黨，選舉只係斷你米路既<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">其中一種比較合法既途徑</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地仲有千千萬萬種方法斷你財路，睇著嚟啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n以下係本人最想大家一起翻譯既網頁、文宣圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PK7FxPg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPK7FxPg.jpg&h=3b5f70d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bwgvaAW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbwgvaAW.jpg&h=1df81a62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YQoJvBp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYQoJvBp.jpg&h=c1bd932d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/27YYjuL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F27YYjuL.jpg&h=c5ee990b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0UuHL9L.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0UuHL9L.gif&h=2b5bbd0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n選舉事實處<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkfactcheck.io/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkfactcheck.io%2F&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpGg5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=cbcc78d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkfactcheck.io/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同我推撚爆呢個PO！！！！！！！！！！！"},{"pid":"02ae7f79024347660088512ee5ba203e462a4060","tid":1747382,"uid":320074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:48:44.000Z","msg":"一推"},{"pid":"df71eba715664e69edf2e5f26f03cfc61f0fe90f","tid":1747382,"uid":320074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:50:38.000Z","msg":"二推"},{"pid":"797722712ac6dccf09d106a3233bc5e225e9cb60","tid":1747382,"uid":320074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T08:10:30.000Z","msg":"P牌既痛苦。。"},{"pid":"201ae4aa9b6efe0cd5c860e811d9fcf102271db8","tid":1747382,"uid":255030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T08:16:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"41ba0ce34997663e9dc8443ef90642e0a70bbb2d","tid":1747382,"uid":320074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"201ae4aa9b6efe0cd5c860e811d9fcf102271db